 &#160;&#160;&#160;id (Optional[str]): Registry database ID. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;key (Optional[str]): Registry database key. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;rev (Optional[str]): Registry database revision. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;filename (Optional[str]): Filename containing dimension records. Only assigned for user input and output purposes. The registry database stores records in the dimension JSON document. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;file_hash (Optional[str]): Hash of the contents of the file. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;records (list[]): Dimension records in filename that get loaded at runtime. Default is [].
